Buba allots 70 . 9 bln dmk in repos , adds funds . The Bundesbank said on Wednesday it has allocated 70 . 9 billion marks of securities repurchase funds at this week ' s tender at a fixed rate of 3 . 0 percent . The German central bank accepted 28 . 9 percent of the bids made for the 14 - day funds . A repo pact for 69 . 6 billion marks at a fixed 3 . 0 percent rate expires on Wednesday , so a net 1 . 3 billion marks is flowing into the market . The Bundesbank said banks bid for 245 . 5 billion marks of the repurchase funds this week . - - Frankfurt Newsroom + 49 69 756525 
